subject: Football (College)
organizations: Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University
lead_paragraph: Adoree’ Jackson scored on a 98-yard kickoff return and a 71-yard pass from Cody Kessler, and No. 24 Southern California blew most of an 18-point third-quarter lead before beating No. 25 Nebraska.
